product_name: LancomeCils Booster XL Vitamin-Infused Lash Thickening Mascara Primer
summary: SummaryLancôme Cils Booster lash primer evenly separates and coats eyelashes with a nourishing, conditioning formula to maximize the results of your mascara. Infused with micro-fibers and vitamin E, this lash primer helps improve natural lash length, thickness, and curl over time for a false lash effect.
details: DetailsFeaturesThe #1 lash-conditioner and mascara primer all-in-one. Now in travel size!Thick, voluminous, healthy lashes can be yours with just one sweep of this innovative mascara primer.Gliding on smoothly and evenly, each coat creates an even surface layer to maximize the results of your favorite mascara by creating the look of fake eyelashes.With a conditioning formula for visible performance, infused with micro-fibers, vitamin B5 and vitamin E, lashes appear longer and fuller by separating individual lashes to maximize volume.This revitalizing lash primer will improve lash thickness and curl over time.White in color, Lancôme's Cils Booster XL Vitamin-Infused Mascara Primer leaves lashes feeling luxurious and soft, while allowing the pigment of your favorite mascara to stand out for a dramatic eye makeup look.This creamy and conditioning formula, not only lengthens and thickens lashes, but can also be worn overnight as a "lash mask."Incorporate into your eye care routine by applying onto clean lashes to nourish and rejuvenate before bed.Beauty Tip: Apply the luxurious Rénergie Lift Multi-Action Eye Cream before using Cils Booster XL for a youthful, radiant, wide-eyed look.BenefitsWorks as a lash conditioner to nourish and condition eyelashes, while maximizing volumeDoubles as a lash primer by coating clean eyelashes smoothly, to provide an ideal mascara base for clump-free applicationIn a consumer test on a panel of 103 women using Cils Booster with their daily mascara:93% of consumers saw more length92% of consumers saw more volume85% of consumers saw more curlItem 2278968How To UseAs A Base Coat For Mascara:Apply from roots to tips of eyelashes. Do not wait until Cils Booster XL is dry before coating lashes with mascara.Coat lashes with mascara for desired look, or until white primer is no long visible.For a optimal color, intensity and a false-lash look, apply two coats of eyelash primer to bottom and top lashes, before applying mascara.As A Nighttime Eyelash Conditioner:After cleansing face, apply Cils Booster XL to bare lashes.Allow to dry properly before sleep.Store in a cool, dry place.IngredientsAqua / Water / Eau, Oryza Sativa Cera / Rice Bran Wax, Copernicia Cerifera Cera / Carnauba Wax / Cire De Carnauba, Cera Alba / Beeswax / Cire Dabeille, Stearic Acid, Candelilla Cera / Candelilla Wax / Cire De Candelilla, Triethanolamine, Palmitic Acid, Acacia Senegal / Acacia Senegal Gum, Panthenol, PEG/PPG-17/18 Dimethicone, Sodium Polymethacrylate, Myristic Acid, Rayon, Hydroxyethylcellulose, Polycaprolactone, Polyquaternium-10, Tocopheryl Acetate, Methylparaben, Propylparaben.Shipping & Coupon RestrictionsThis brand is excluded from most Ulta Beauty coupons.See brand eligibility details
how_to_use: As A Base Coat For Mascara:Apply from roots to tips of eyelashes. Do not wait until Cils Booster XL is dry before coating lashes with mascara.Coat lashes with mascara for desired look, or until white primer is no long visible.For a optimal color, intensity and a false-lash look, apply two coats of eyelash primer to bottom and top lashes, before applying mascara.As A Nighttime Eyelash Conditioner:After cleansing face, apply Cils Booster XL to bare lashes.Allow to dry properly before sleep.Store in a cool, dry place.

reviews.headline: Life changing!
reviews.comments: I have been using this everyday for atleast 6 years and I seriously could not imagine my makeup routine without it. This makes the biggest difference in the appearance of my mascara, the volume and curl of my eyelashes, and the longevity of my mascara. If I ever forget to apply, I can immediately tell the second I put my mascara on because it looks so different without it. I would start over and use the primer!! Thats how important this is to me. Seriously could not recommend a product more. It has changed my life!!!!!!!!

faceoff_positive.comments:
I have medium length lashes, not very full. The Cils Booster XL glides on smoothly, already lengthening my lashes. And then when I apply the mascara, oh wow, long lashes I wasn't born with! And it stays good and clean all day, no clumping. Sometimes I used to have dark smudges by the end of the day, but now it doesn't happen unless I get teary eyed. I gave a tube to a friend and she is still singing its praises. Thank you Lancome, what a great product.

Note: Don't let the Cil Booster XL dry before you put on your mascara, or it will clump. Do one eye at a time. I got this tip from Lancome online support. Unfortunately the product didn't come with instructions. :- /
faceoff_positive.headline: Works!!

faceoff_negative.comments: I have dark, medium length lashes on the thinner side. I've applied this using multiple mascaras and have noticed no difference. I've applied the mascara while the Cils Booster was still wet and waited for it to dry also, but the result was the same. I've noticed no increase in length or volume when using this product. In fact, I think it makes my lashes more clumped together than any thing else. I don't understand all of the good reviews. I just must not have the appropriate lash type for this product.
faceoff_negative.headline: I didn't notice anything
